# Placeholder file. Actual nfqws binaries should be placed in:
# - binaries/arm64/nfqws (arm64-v8a)
# - binaries/arm/nfqws (armeabi-v7a)
# - binaries/x86_64/nfqws (x86_64)
# - binaries/x86/nfqws (x86)
#
# Build nfqws from the Zapret repository:
# https://github.com/bol-van/zapret
#
# Cross-compile using Android NDK:
#   $ANDROID_NDK/toolchains/llvm/prebuilt/windows-x86_64/bin/aarch64-linux-android29-clang \
#       -o nfqws nfqws.c -lnetfilter_queue
